article_title: Dwayne Johnson: Maybe I'll run for president
article_text:
Actor Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson is leaving the door open to wrestling his way to the presidency some day.

"Cool piece on why I should run for President," Johnson tweeted Friday, linking to a story about his potential political appeal.

article_metadata.dcterms.description: "Surely the White House has a spot for my pick up truck."
